  "subject": [],
  "abstracts": [
    {
      "note": "",
      "abstract": "Relates to authorizing and regulating the use of electronic bell jar vending machines; requires responsible placement and operation of electronic bell jar vending machines; allows for geographic considerations for such machine placement."
